invisAD-client - Automatic openSUSE Client Integration

The scripts in this package helps you to integrate an openSUSE based computer
to an ActiveDirectory on an invis-Server.

The scripts:

1. joininvis - Joins the AD Domain and mounts the invis-servers fileserver 
   shares via NFS on the client computer. This script is needet only one time.
   
2. delssscache - Removes an existing sssd-cache completely. This script is 
   needed in case if user mapping and enumerating didn't work properly.

3. invisconnect - This script connects an client computer via OpenVPN to an
   invis-Server.
   
This scripts of this package only works on openSUSE based systems.

Have a lot of fun....

Stefan - invis-server.org
